ygData.messageBody:
Hey! I was/am in that Guild!! and Kirei sounds familiar...Monk? I signed on
there once about oh 3 months ago & was told about a split, and for that
moment I talked'em out of it (since the leader of the split said 90% of the

amazons, besides! what better tag is ther than Amazons of Norrath! hehee
sorry guys)
it was still together a few weeks ago...oh, and all female toons, not
players, lots of straight guys who want to make cracks about butt cleavage,
again, back when I was an active member...

Melanie-
